===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ˈspæŋk/}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æŋk|-æŋk]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To smack or slap a person's buttocks with the bare hand or other object, as punishment or as a form of sexual interaction.
#: ''My father used to put me over his knee and '''spank''' my bare bum when I was a bad girl.''     
# To soundly defeat, to [[trounce]].
# To move rapidly.
#: ''The ship was really spanking along.''

